<tr id="L399"><td><a href="#L399">399</a></td><td>O'BRIEN:  I am not guilty. I have committed no crime, and I do not concede to this court or the Cardassian Empire.</td></tr>

<tr id="L400"><td><a href="#L400">400</a></td><td>KOVAT:  Madam Archon, I apologise but I appear I have lost control of my client.</td></tr>

